	   <tr><td colspan=2>I see that there are many questions, but almost no answers. Well i wanna solve that.=')<br><br>1)Pull with darkness so they run slowly to ya.<br>2) If you can try putting your strongest Raw damage DOT on them (heat blood/Boil Blood) Before they reach you(if you can).<br>3) Chances are that by the time you put on your Second DOT he has already hit you, so your pet is on him. If not then send pet.<br>4) Fear him if he is even Yellow or red. Because  after your next DOT he will agro on YOU! And your a caster... NO AC. The MoB will light you up.<br>5) while hes feared put on your next cool DOT... Leach or a heart flutter type. Your pet will probobly be pounding away at his back.<br>6) By this time he should be dead... But if he is not then try your Siphon Stregnth, or Shadow vortex. If it is Undead then use Ward/Expuls/ect. undead on it till its dead. AND KEEP IT FEARED IF IT IS EVEN,YELLOW, OR RED.<br><br>Tip:If something else decides to attack you and you cant kill them both, then use fieghn death to make a quik excape.<br><br>There thats all folks. Good luck to everyone. And dont play in Char if you can help it when ur a necro.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
